## Opis

Zero-Day Research Laboratory je enterprise-grade platforma za odkrivanje in raziskovanje neznanih ranljivosti (zero-day), vključno z vulnerability research, exploit development in responsible disclosure.

## Vključene komponente

### Vulnerability Research
- Target analysis
- Attack surface mapping
- Code auditing
- Fuzzing infrastructure
- Symbolic execution
- Taint analysis

### Fuzzing Infrastructure
- Coverage-guided fuzzing
- Grammar-based fuzzing
- Protocol fuzzing
- API fuzzing
- Kernel fuzzing
- Browser fuzzing

### Exploit Development
- Vulnerability analysis
- Exploit primitives
- Payload development
- Bypass techniques
- Reliability engineering
- Weaponization

### Proof of Concept
- PoC development
- Impact demonstration
- Reproducibility
- Documentation
- Video evidence

### Responsible Disclosure
- Vendor notification
- Coordination timeline
- Patch verification
- Public disclosure
- CVE assignment

### Research Tools
- Debuggers (x64dbg, WinDbg, GDB)
- Disassemblers (IDA, Ghidra, Binary Ninja)
- Emulators (QEMU, Unicorn)
- Instrumentation (Frida, DynamoRIO)
- Symbolic execution (angr, KLEE)

